OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have stay dry
OL,6,Fthrough the day with some prolonged
OL,7,Fsunny intervals though this turning
OL,8,Fhazy at times with some variable
OL,9,Fcloud. Mainly light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe evening will start dry,
OL,12,Fbut cloud and rain will soon spread
OL,13,Feast to all parts, turning heavier for
OL,14,Fa time overnight. Clearer spells and
OL,15,Fshowers in northwest by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
