OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAny remaining overnight rain
OL,6,Fwill soon clear east then sunny spells
OL,7,Fand showers. Drier for a time in the
OL,8,Fafternoon before further showers
OL,9,Flater, heavy at times. Cool and
OL,10,Fblustery.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,13,Fcold and unsettled Wednesday and
OL,14,FThursday with scattered showers.
OL,15,FChance of overnight frost. Mostly dry
OL,16,Fand bright on Friday but evening rain
OL,17,Fpossible in far northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
